			<h1>Introduction</h1>
Everyone loves cupcakes! They're one of the sweetest pick-me-ups and delicious desserts out there. So whenever your craving something sweet, why not bake a cupcake! It's a fun activity, fulfilling, rewarding and definitely satisfying. What's more is that if you bake it yourself, you know all the ingredients that's going to be used and maybe even control the proportions. That's why Cupcake Cure offers easy-to-follow cupcake recipes that you can bake right in your kitchen. We're also aware that cupcakes aren't the healthiest option for a dessert but it is a luxury that we can reward ourselves with. For this reason, we make sure to post the nutritional information of the cupcake so you know exactly how to fit it into your daily calorie budget. We are also very health-conscious and we also want to promote a healthy lifestyle into our website. Feel free to read our health-related articles and use some tools like our calorie calculator to find out how many calories you need daily. So go ahead and view our recipes, available in written and slideshow instructions. After that maybe you'd like to check out our drool-worthy picture gallery and look at the many other things we offer! We hope you enjoy yourself and find this website very informative, entertaining as well as enjoyable. Just navigate the site through the links above and if you're having troubles with our links, view our <a href="sitemap.php">site map</a> instead. Let's start baking!

